    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "REPLACE_WITH_AGENT_EMAIL",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "={{ $json.name }}, one week on — still thinking about {{ $json.property_address }}?",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<html><body style=\"font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc;\">\n<div style=\"background: white; padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; border-top: 4px solid #dc2626;\">\n  <h2 style=\"color: #0f172a;\">Still on the fence, {{ $json.name }}? 🤔</h2>\n  <p>It's been a week since you visited <strong>{{ $json.property_address }}</strong>. The seller has been receiving increased interest this week.</p>\n  <div style=\"background: #fef2f2; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0; color: #991b1b;\"><strong>⚡ Market update:</strong> Properties in this area are averaging REPLACE_WITH_AVG_DAYS_ON_MARKET days on the market. Don't miss out!</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>I'd love to jump on a quick 15-minute call to answer any remaining questions and help you move forward with confidence:</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 28px 0;\">\n    <a href=\"REPLACE_WITH_CALENDLY_URL\" style=\"background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">📞 Book a 15-Min Call</a>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"color: #64748b;\">Not the right fit? No problem — I work with buyers every day and would love to help you find your perfect home. Just hit reply and let me know what you're really looking for.</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px;\">— REPLACE_WITH_AGENT_NAME | REPLACE_WITH_AGENT_PHONE | REPLACE_WITH_AGENCY_NAME</p>\n</div>\n</body></html>",
        "options": {}
      },
